project_descr: The Promoting Sustainable Bio-energy Production from Biomass (SBEPB) Project is contributing to the reduction of greenhouse emissions through removal of barriers to sustainable production and utilization of biomass resources in Timor-Leste

outputs.output_descr: Objective: Removal of barriers to sustainable production and utilization of biomass resources in Timor-Leste and application of biomass energy technologies to support local economic, environmental and social development that leads to GHG mitigation.
